update.packages() has several arguments.  As my previous email said, the
library paths seen by R can have __different sources__ on Debian system so
you have to __treat them differently__.

So

    update.packages(lib.loc="/usr/local/lib/R/site-library", checkBuilt=TRUE)

may be what you wanted here.
 
